Launch ec2 instance.
2)	Click on launch instance.
3)	Select AMI and key.
4)	In security group ssh (22), http (80).
5)	Take ssh of instance and go to instance.
6)	Update the system(sudo yum update).
7)	Install nginx service(sudo yum install nginx).
8)	Start nginx service(sudo systemctl start nginx).
9)	Enable nginx service(sudo systemctl enable nginx).
10)	Install mysql[mariadb] service(sudo yum install mariadb105-server.x86_64.
11)	Start mariadb service(sudo systemctl start mariadb.service).
12)	Enable mariadb service(sudo systemctl enable mariadb.service).
13)	Install php service(sudo yum install php8.1.x86_64 â€“y).
14)	Start php service(sudo systemctl start php-fpm.service).
15)	Enable php service(sudo systemctl enable php-fpm.service).
16)	To create information php page in nginx.
17)	Change directory to nginx in the html(cd /usr/share/nginx/html).
18)	Here we have create information page of php(sudo vim info.php).
19)	We have write in the php file be like.
<? 
Php phpinfo();
?>
20)	Save this file (:wq!).
21)	Restart the nginx service(sudo systemctl restart nginx).
22)	Check on browser it is working or not for this copy public address.
23)	Nginx page will load for checking information page of php(public_ip/info.php).
24)	It will show php information page on browser. 

